----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  A) TestGear1.lha & TestGear1.readme:-
  -------------------------------------

  (Last issue date 1-5-2002, Version 1.00.25.)

  1) TestCard Generator. OPTIONAL CABLE ASSEMBLY, STANDARD TV LEAD SUPPLIED.
     (NOTE:- ~TestCard.lha~ is a complete archive of this project including
     a complete ~PC~ version and the ~Source Code~ for both.)
  2) Signal Injector. SIMPLE CABLE ASSEMBLY.
  3) Sine/Square Generator. EVEN SIMPLER CABLE ASSEMBLY.
  4) Pulse Generator. SIMPLE STRIPBOARD AND CABLE ASSEMBLY.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  B) TestGear2.lha & TestGear2.readme:-
  -------------------------------------

  (Last issue date 23-11-2001, Version 3.00.15.)

  5) Stereo LF Audio Function Generator. TWO SIMPLE CABLE ASSEMBLIES.
  6) Analogue To Digital Converter. SIMPLE EUROCARD ASSEMBLY.
  7) Audio Power Meter. SIMPLE ELECTRONIC AND MECHANICAL ASSEMBLY.
  8) RF Probe, (Sniffer). SIMPLE STRIPBOARD AND MECHANICAL ASSEMBLY.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  C) TestGear3.lha & TestGear3.readme:-
  -------------------------------------

  (Last issue date 1-4-2001, Version 3.10.10.)

  9) Logic Probe. SIMPLE CABLE ASSEMBLY.
 9A) Experimental Version Of Project9. NO CONSTRUCTIONAL DETAILS.
 10) An Absorption RF Wattmeter. STRICT CONSTRUCTION DETAILS.
 11) An Oscilloscope Calibrator. FULL CONSTRUCTIONAL INFORMATION.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  D1) TestGear4B.lha & TestGear4B.readme:-
  ----------------------------------------

  (Last issue date 1-12-2001, Version 3.00.20.)

 12) Oscilloscope, DC to 100KHz (Storage). SOFTWARE NOW COMPLETED.
     HARDWARE BUILT IN 3 STAGES. ALL OF THE STAGES ARE COMPLETED.
     THIS IS FOR THE EXPERIENCED CONSTRUCTOR, ALL OF THE ELECTRONICS
     ARE HARD WIRED THEREFORE NO PRINTED CIRCUITS ARE USED.

   Stage1) Initial construction stage.
   Stage2) Next stage.
   Stage3) The final stage.

  D2) TestGear4A.lha & TestGear4A.readme:-
  ----------------------------------------
 
 Scope) The running software.

  D3) TestGear4C.lha & TestGear4C.readme:-
  ----------------------------------------

 PCB-Layouts) Empty at the moment. THIS IS LEFT OPEN FOR ANYONE WHO WANTS
              TO DESIGN A PCB AS I AM NOT INTERESTED IN DOING SO.

  D4) TestGear4D.lha & TestGear4D.readme:-
  ----------------------------------------

 Pictures) HAM Photo(s) of the project.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  E) TestGear5.lha & TestGear5.readme:-
  -------------------------------------

  (Last issue date 1-1-2003, Version 3.00.00.)

 13) An Eight Channel Logic Analyser. STRIPBOARD AND CABLE ASSEMBLY, THIRD
     PARTY SOFTWARE INCLUDED.
 14) A Games Port 10 MHz Frequency Counter. STRIPBOARD AND CABLE ASSEMBLY,
     EXPERIMENTAL HIGH GAIN WIDE BAND AMPLIFIER CIRCUIT INCLUDED.
 15) Dual Games Port A-D Converter. STRIPBOARD AND CABLE ASSEMBLY.

