----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Testing Evaluation:-
    --------------------

    All projects were intended for use with both NTSC and PAL in mind.

    I have received many Emails confirming that the projects to ~Project11~
    work on just about every AMIGA setup and OS available today, including a
    CDTV. This includes graphics cards, accelerators, extra memory etc...
    and with the correct parallel port cable assembly, an A1000.

